{"paragraphs":[{"cues":[{"time":693,"text":"I'm going to ask and try to answer,"},{"time":2948,"text":"in some ways, kind of an uncomfortable question."},{"time":7846,"text":"Both civilians, obviously, and soldiers"},{"time":10200,"text":"suffer in war;"},{"time":12286,"text":"I don't think any civilian has ever missed"},{"time":14750,"text":"the war that they were subjected to."},{"time":18112,"text":"I've been covering wars for almost 20 years,"},{"time":20130,"text":"and one of the remarkable things for me"},{"time":23458,"text":"is how many soldiers find themselves missing it."},{"time":27342,"text":"How is it someone can go through"},{"time":29647,"text":"the worst experience imaginable,"},{"time":31984,"text":"and come home, back to their home,"},{"time":33960,"text":"and their family, their country, and miss the war?"},{"time":37421,"text":"How does that work? What does it mean?"},{"time":40992,"text":"We have to answer that question,"},{"time":44450,"text":"because if we don't, it'll be impossible"},{"time":47317,"text":"to bring soldiers back"},{"time":48585,"text":"to a place in society where they belong,"},{"time":52640,"text":"and I think it'll also be impossible to stop war,"},{"time":54893,"text":"if we don't understand how that mechanism works."}]},{"cues":[{"time":57911,"text":"The problem is that war"},{"time":61173,"text":"does not have a simple, neat truth,"},{"time":65010,"text":"one simple, neat truth."}]},{"cues":[{"time":67709,"text":"Any sane person hates war,"},{"time":69970,"text":"hates the idea of war,"},{"time":71825,"text":"wouldn't want to have anything to do with it,"},{"time":74402,"text":"doesn't want to be near it,\ndoesn't want to know about it."},{"time":77518,"text":"That's a sane response to war."},{"time":80202,"text":"But if I asked all of you in this room,"},{"time":82969,"text":"who here has paid money"},{"time":86327,"text":"to go to a cinema"},{"time":88313,"text":"and be entertained by a Hollywood war movie,"},{"time":91703,"text":"most of you would probably raise your hands."},{"time":95261,"text":"That's what's so complicated about war."},{"time":97857,"text":"And trust me, if a room full of peace-loving people"},{"time":101397,"text":"finds something compelling about war,"},{"time":104636,"text":"so do 20-year-old soldiers"},{"time":107379,"text":"who have been trained in it, I promise you."},{"time":110641,"text":"That's the thing that has to be understood."}]},{"cues":[{"time":113945,"text":"I've covered war for about 20 years, as I said,"},{"time":116767,"text":"but my most intense experiences in combat"},{"time":119393,"text":"were with American soldiers in Afghanistan."},{"time":123625,"text":"I've been in Africa, the Middle East,"},{"time":124940,"text":"Afghanistan in the '90s,"},{"time":126690,"text":"but it was with American soldiers in 2007, 2008,"},{"time":130537,"text":"that I was confronted with"},{"time":133170,"text":"very intense combat."},{"time":134690,"text":"I was in a small valley called the Korengal Valley"},{"time":136730,"text":"in eastern Afghanistan."},{"time":139563,"text":"It was six miles long."},{"time":141349,"text":"There were 150 men of\nBattle Company in that valley,"},{"time":144491,"text":"and for a while, while I was there,"},{"time":148025,"text":"almost 20 percent of all the combat"},{"time":150301,"text":"in all of Afghanistan was happening"},{"time":152097,"text":"in those six miles."},{"time":153930,"text":"A hundred and fifty men were absorbing"},{"time":156481,"text":"almost a fifth of the combat for all of NATO forces"},{"time":159633,"text":"in the country, for a couple months."},{"time":162159,"text":"It was very intense."},{"time":164296,"text":"I spent most of my time at a small outpost"},{"time":166365,"text":"called Restrepo."},{"time":167939,"text":"It was named after the platoon medic"},{"time":169499,"text":"that had been killed about two\nmonths into the deployment."},{"time":172353,"text":"It was a few plywood B-huts"},{"time":176293,"text":"clinging to a side of a ridge,"},{"time":180102,"text":"and sandbags, bunkers, gun positions,"},{"time":184879,"text":"and there were 20 men up there"},{"time":186690,"text":"of Second Platoon, Battle Company."},{"time":188775,"text":"I spent most of my time up there."},{"time":190375,"text":"There was no running water."},{"time":191990,"text":"There was no way to bathe."},{"time":193001,"text":"The guys were up there for a month at a time."},{"time":195440,"text":"They never even got out of their clothes."},{"time":197964,"text":"They fought. The worked."},{"time":199114,"text":"They slept in the same clothes."},{"time":201860,"text":"They never took them off,\nand at the end of the month,"},{"time":203339,"text":"they went back down to the company headquarters,"},{"time":205650,"text":"and by then, their clothes were unwearable."},{"time":207717,"text":"They burned them and got a new set."},{"time":210010,"text":"There was no Internet. There was no phone."},{"time":211730,"text":"There was no communication\nwith the outside world up there."},{"time":215629,"text":"There was no cooked food."},{"time":218459,"text":"There was nothing up there"},{"time":221030,"text":"that young men typically like:"},{"time":222930,"text":"no cars, no girls, no television, nothing"},{"time":226211,"text":"except combat."},{"time":228075,"text":"Combat they did learn to like."}]},{"cues":[{"time":232036,"text":"I remember one day, it was a very hot day"},{"time":234487,"text":"in the spring,"},{"time":236253,"text":"and we hadn't been in a fight"},{"time":238634,"text":"in a couple of weeks, maybe."},{"time":241080,"text":"Usually, the outpost was attacked,"},{"time":243644,"text":"and we hadn't seen any\ncombat in a couple of weeks,"},{"time":246507,"text":"and everyone was just stunned"},{"time":249110,"text":"with boredom and heat."},{"time":251267,"text":"And I remember the lieutenant walking past me"},{"time":255801,"text":"sort of stripped to the waist."},{"time":257274,"text":"It was incredibly hot."},{"time":259676,"text":"Stripped to the waist, walked past me muttering,"},{"time":262040,"text":"\"Oh God, please someone attack us today.\""},{"time":264792,"text":"That's how bored they were."},{"time":267142,"text":"That's war too, is a lieutenant saying,"},{"time":270208,"text":"\"Please make something happen"},{"time":272868,"text":"because we're going crazy.\""}]},{"cues":[{"time":274911,"text":"To understand that,"},{"time":277259,"text":"you have to, for a moment,"},{"time":279169,"text":"think about combat not morally --"},{"time":281570,"text":"that's an important job to do â€”"},{"time":283455,"text":"but for a moment, don't think about it morally,"},{"time":285348,"text":"think about it neurologically."},{"time":288219,"text":"Let's think about what happens in your brain"},{"time":290431,"text":"when you're in combat."},{"time":292804,"text":"First of all, the experience"},{"time":295156,"text":"is very bizarre, it's a very bizarre one."},{"time":299770,"text":"It's not what I had expected."},{"time":302760,"text":"Usually, you're not scared."},{"time":304490,"text":"I've been very scared in combat,"},{"time":306610,"text":"but most of the time when I was out there,"},{"time":308712,"text":"I wasn't scared."},{"time":309839,"text":"I was very scared beforehand"},{"time":311366,"text":"and incredibly scared afterwards,"},{"time":313281,"text":"and that fear that comes afterwards can last years."},{"time":315883,"text":"I haven't been shot at in six years,"},{"time":317835,"text":"and I was woken up very abruptly this morning"},{"time":320188,"text":"by a nightmare that I was being strafed by aircraft,"},{"time":323433,"text":"six years later."},{"time":324640,"text":"I've never even been strafed by aircraft,"},{"time":326374,"text":"and I was having nightmares about it."},{"time":329750,"text":"Time slows down."},{"time":331123,"text":"You get this weird tunnel vision."},{"time":333347,"text":"You notice some details very, very, very accurately"},{"time":337008,"text":"and other things drop out."},{"time":339195,"text":"It's almost a slightly altered state of mind."},{"time":342158,"text":"What's happening in your brain"},{"time":343629,"text":"is you're getting an enormous amount of adrenaline"},{"time":346346,"text":"pumped through your system."},{"time":348166,"text":"Young men will go to great lengths"},{"time":350760,"text":"to have that experience."},{"time":353096,"text":"It's wired into us."},{"time":356018,"text":"It's hormonally supported."},{"time":359860,"text":"The mortality rate for young men in society"},{"time":363745,"text":"is six times what it is for young women"},{"time":366165,"text":"from violence and from accidents,"},{"time":367970,"text":"just the stupid stuff that young men do:"},{"time":370159,"text":"jumping off of things they shouldn't jump off of,"},{"time":372461,"text":"lighting things on fire they shouldn't light on fire,"},{"time":374880,"text":"I mean, you know what I'm talking about."},{"time":377118,"text":"They die at six times the rate"},{"time":379159,"text":"that young women do."},{"time":380599,"text":"Statistically, you are safer as a teenage boy,"},{"time":384503,"text":"you would be safer in the fire department"},{"time":387146,"text":"or the police department in most American cities"},{"time":389710,"text":"than just walking around the\nstreets of your hometown"},{"time":392232,"text":"looking for something to do,"},{"time":394590,"text":"statistically."}]},{"cues":[{"time":397650,"text":"You can imagine how that plays out in combat."},{"time":400888,"text":"At Restrepo, every guy up there was almost killed,"},{"time":403950,"text":"including me,"},{"time":405644,"text":"including my good friend Tim Hetherington,"},{"time":407704,"text":"who was later killed in Libya."},{"time":410126,"text":"There were guys walking around"},{"time":411802,"text":"with bullet holes in their uniforms,"},{"time":413623,"text":"rounds that had cut through the fabric"},{"time":415510,"text":"and didn't touch their bodies."}]},{"cues":[{"time":418892,"text":"I was leaning against some sandbags one morning,"},{"time":421974,"text":"not much going on, sort of spacing out,"},{"time":424971,"text":"and some sand was kicked into the side of,"},{"time":428478,"text":"sort of hit the side of my face."},{"time":431148,"text":"Something hit the side of my face,\nand I didn't know what it was."},{"time":433361,"text":"You have to understand about bullets"},{"time":434900,"text":"that they go a lot faster than sound,"},{"time":436798,"text":"so if someone shoots at you"},{"time":438211,"text":"from a few hundred meters,"},{"time":440268,"text":"the bullet goes by you, or hits you obviously,"},{"time":443411,"text":"half a second or so before\nthe sound catches up to it."},{"time":446063,"text":"So I had some sand sprayed in the side of my face."},{"time":448950,"text":"Half a second later, I heard dut-dut-dut-dut-duh."},{"time":450950,"text":"It was machine gun fire."},{"time":451964,"text":"It was the first round, the first burst"},{"time":454310,"text":"of an hour-long firefight."},{"time":457173,"text":"What had happened was the bullet hit,"},{"time":460238,"text":"a bullet hit three or four inches\nfrom the side of my head."},{"time":463981,"text":"Imagine, just think about it, because I certainly did,"},{"time":468630,"text":"think about the angle of deviation that saved my life."},{"time":470510,"text":"At 400 meters, it missed me by three inches."},{"time":472972,"text":"Just think about the math on that."},{"time":477268,"text":"Every guy up there"},{"time":479052,"text":"had some experience like that,"},{"time":480974,"text":"at least once, if not many times."}]},{"cues":[{"time":484502,"text":"The boys are up there for a year."},{"time":486982,"text":"They got back."},{"time":488751,"text":"Some of them got out of the Army"},{"time":490110,"text":"and had tremendous psychological\nproblems when they got home."},{"time":492704,"text":"Some of them stayed in the Army"},{"time":494239,"text":"and were more or less okay, psychologically."},{"time":497862,"text":"I was particularly close to a\nguy named Brendan O'Byrne."},{"time":500939,"text":"I'm still very good friends with him."},{"time":502827,"text":"He came back to the States. He got out of the Army."},{"time":505883,"text":"I had a dinner party one night."},{"time":507851,"text":"I invited him,"},{"time":509645,"text":"and he started talking with a woman,"},{"time":513080,"text":"one of my friends,"},{"time":514317,"text":"and she knew how bad it had been out there,"},{"time":517369,"text":"and she said, \"Brendan,"},{"time":519118,"text":"is there anything at all that you miss about"},{"time":522446,"text":"being out in Afghanistan, about the war?\""},{"time":526000,"text":"And he thought about it quite a long time,"},{"time":529169,"text":"and finally he said, \"Ma'am, I miss almost all of it.\""},{"time":534552,"text":"And he's one of the most traumatized people"},{"time":537994,"text":"I've seen from that war."},{"time":541083,"text":"\"Ma'am, I miss almost all of it.\""}]},{"cues":[{"time":543094,"text":"What is he talking about?"},{"time":546179,"text":"He's not a psychopath."},{"time":549621,"text":"He doesn't miss killing people."},{"time":551280,"text":"He's not crazy. He doesn't miss getting shot at"},{"time":553560,"text":"and seeing his friends get killed."},{"time":555262,"text":"What is it that he misses? We have to answer that."},{"time":559090,"text":"If we're going to stop war, we\nhave to answer that question."}]},{"cues":[{"time":565816,"text":"I think what he missed is brotherhood."},{"time":570994,"text":"He missed, in some ways,"},{"time":572750,"text":"the opposite of killing."},{"time":574146,"text":"What he missed was connection"},{"time":576478,"text":"to the other men he was with."},{"time":578826,"text":"Now, brotherhood is different from friendship."},{"time":581342,"text":"Friendship happens in society, obviously."},{"time":585096,"text":"The more you like someone,"},{"time":586634,"text":"the more you'd be willing to do for them."},{"time":588708,"text":"Brotherhood has nothing to do"},{"time":590214,"text":"with how you feel about the other person."},{"time":593706,"text":"It's a mutual agreement in a group"},{"time":596688,"text":"that you will put the welfare of the group,"},{"time":598930,"text":"you will put the safety of everyone in the group"},{"time":600950,"text":"above your own."},{"time":602810,"text":"In effect, you're saying,"},{"time":606187,"text":"\"I love these other people more than I love myself.\""}]},{"cues":[{"time":611602,"text":"Brendan was a team leader"},{"time":613000,"text":"in command of three men,"},{"time":614863,"text":"and the worst day in Afghanistan â€”"},{"time":618300,"text":"He was almost killed so many times."},{"time":621179,"text":"It didn't bother him."},{"time":622514,"text":"The worst thing that happened to him in Afghanistan"},{"time":625092,"text":"was one of his men was hit in the head with a bullet"},{"time":627908,"text":"in the helmet, knocked him over."},{"time":632392,"text":"They thought he was dead."},{"time":633520,"text":"It was in the middle of a huge firefight."},{"time":634970,"text":"No one could deal with it, and a minute later,"},{"time":636990,"text":"Kyle Steiner sat back up"},{"time":639030,"text":"from the dead, as it were,"},{"time":640955,"text":"because he'd come back to consciousness."},{"time":642980,"text":"The bullet had just knocked him out."},{"time":644252,"text":"It glanced off the helmet."},{"time":646179,"text":"He remembers people saying,"},{"time":648245,"text":"as he was sort of half-conscious,"},{"time":649707,"text":"he remembers people saying,"},{"time":653206,"text":"\"Steiner's been hit in the head. Steiner's dead.\""},{"time":655277,"text":"And he was thinking, \"I'm not dead.\""},{"time":656899,"text":"And he sat up."},{"time":658647,"text":"And Brendan realized after that"},{"time":660844,"text":"that he could not protect his men,"},{"time":662485,"text":"and that was the only time he cried in Afghanistan,"},{"time":664863,"text":"was realizing that."},{"time":667828,"text":"That's brotherhood."}]},{"cues":[{"time":670340,"text":"This wasn't invented recently."},{"time":672772,"text":"Many of you have probably read \"The Iliad.\""},{"time":675269,"text":"Achilles surely would have risked his life"},{"time":677240,"text":"or given his life to save his friend Patroclus."},{"time":682018,"text":"In World War II, there were many stories"},{"time":684956,"text":"of soldiers who were wounded,"},{"time":688032,"text":"were brought to a rear base hospital,"},{"time":690099,"text":"who went AWOL,"},{"time":691455,"text":"crawled out of windows, slipped out doors,"},{"time":693675,"text":"went AWOL, wounded,"},{"time":697273,"text":"to make their way back to the front lines"},{"time":698675,"text":"to rejoin their brothers out there."},{"time":701311,"text":"So you think about Brendan,"},{"time":703660,"text":"you think about all these soldiers"},{"time":707016,"text":"having an experience like that, a bond like that,"},{"time":709901,"text":"in a small group,"},{"time":711781,"text":"where they loved 20 other people"},{"time":713679,"text":"in some ways more than they loved themselves,"},{"time":716598,"text":"you think about how good that would feel, imagine it,"},{"time":721714,"text":"and they are blessed with that experience for a year,"},{"time":726344,"text":"and then they come home,"},{"time":727833,"text":"and they are just back in society"},{"time":730820,"text":"like the rest of us are,"},{"time":733659,"text":"not knowing who they can count on,"},{"time":736085,"text":"not knowing who loves them, who they can love,"},{"time":741262,"text":"not knowing exactly what anyone they know"},{"time":743853,"text":"would do for them if it came down to it."},{"time":746087,"text":"That is terrifying."},{"time":749673,"text":"Compared to that,"},{"time":751663,"text":"war, psychologically, in some ways, is easy,"},{"time":755737,"text":"compared to that kind of alienation."},{"time":758234,"text":"That's why they miss it,"},{"time":759624,"text":"and that's what we have to understand"},{"time":762102,"text":"and in some ways fix in our society."}]},{"cues":[{"time":765505,"text":"Thank you very much."}]},{"cues":[{"time":768435,"text":"(Applause)"}]}]}